\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hsm1665702941775.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hsm1665702941775.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hsm1665702941775.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hsm1665702941775\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Informix Error Messages\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"hsm1665702941775__informix_error_messages_153244\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hsm1665702941775__p_d51128e1_d51129e1_d51130e1\">Both connector and Informix DBMS error and warning messages can be seen in the message frame. The connector may report more than one error or warning at a time.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hsm1665702941775__p_d51131e1_d51132e1_d51133e1\">Connector error and warning messages have the following syntax:</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hsm1665702941775__p_d51134e1_d51135e1_d51136e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Connector</code> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">ERROR</code>|<code class=\"ph codeph\">WARNING</code>} (<var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>)<code class=\"ph codeph\">:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Message</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hsm1665702941775__p_d51137e1_d51138e1_d51139e1\">Informix error and warning messages have the following syntax:</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hsm1665702941775__p_d51140e1_d51141e1_d51142e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">Informix</code> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">ERROR</code>|<code class=\"ph codeph\">WARNING</code>|<code class=\"ph codeph\">NO</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">DATA</code>} (<code class=\"ph codeph\">SQLSTATE:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">sqlstate</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">):</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Message</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">SQLCODE</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">sqlcode</var>: <var class=\"keyword varname\">Message</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hsm1665702941775__p_d51143e1_d51144e1_d51145e1\">The last error detected by the connector is available in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$dberror</span>. The possible error messages are listed in the table.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><div class=\"dataTables_wrapper no-footer\" id=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1_wrapper\"><div class=\"dataTables_filter\" id=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1_filter\"><label>Search:<input aria-controls=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1\" class=\"\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"search\"/></label></div><div class=\"zDocsFilterTableDiv false\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Filter columns\" class=\"zDocsTopicPageColumnsButton dropdown-toggle\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\">Column<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-filter\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-filter\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu\"><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-$dberror value-0-0\" id=\"topic-$dberror value-0-0\" name=\"topic-$dberror value-0-0\" type=\"checkbox\"/><label for=\"topic-$dberror value-0-0\">$dberror value</label></div><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-Message-1-0\" id=\"topic-Message-1-0\" name=\"topic-Message-1-0\" type=\"checkbox\"/><label for=\"topic-Message-1-0\">Message</label></div></div><div class=\"searchAllTable\"><label aria-hidden=\"false\" class=\"zDocsInputFieldLabel\" for=\"search-all-smart-table\">Filter results...</label><input aria-label=\"Filter results in the table\" class=\"zDocsInputField\" id=\"search-all-smart-table\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"text\" value=\"\"/><button aria-label=\"Submit\" class=\"zDocsInputFieldSearch\" type=\"submit\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-search\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-search\"></use></svg></button><div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"sr-only\">41 rows found</div></div><div><button aria-label=\"Export table to a file\" class=\"zDocsTopicPageTableExportButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-v\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-v\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicPageTableExportMenu\"><button aria-label=\"Export to Excel\" class=\"dropdown-item\" type=\"button\">Export to Excel</button><button aria-label=\"Export to CSV\" class=\"dropdown-item\" type=\"button\">Export to CSV</button></div></div></div><div class=\"dataTables_scroll\" data-testid=\"sticky-header-table\"><div class=\"dataTables_scrollHead\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; border: 0px; width: 100%;\"><div class=\"dataTables_scrollHeadInner\" style=\"box-sizing: content-box; width: 959px; padding-right: 0px;\"><table class=\"table dataTable no-footer\" count-columns=\"2\" style=\"margin-left: 0px; width: 959px;\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Error values returned in $dberror</span></caption><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\"><th aria-controls=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1\" aria-label=\"\n $dberror value\n : activate to sort column ascending\" class=\"entry sorting\" colspan=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 168.766px;\" tabindex=\"0\">\n $dberror value\n </th><th aria-controls=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1\" aria-label=\"\n Message\n : activate to sort column ascending\" class=\"entry sorting\" colspan=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 739.234px;\" tabindex=\"0\">\n Message\n </th></tr>\n<tr class=\"searchTableDiv\"><td><label aria-hidden=\"false\" class=\"zDocsInputFieldLabel\" for=\"search-$dberror value-0\">Filter</label><input aria-label=\"Filter column\" class=\"zDocsInputField zDocsSearchInTable\" id=\"search-$dberror value-0\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"text\" value=\"\"/><div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"sr-only\">41 rows found</div></td><td><label aria-hidden=\"false\" class=\"zDocsInputFieldLabel\" for=\"search-Message-1\">Filter</label><input aria-label=\"Filter column\" class=\"zDocsInputField zDocsSearchInTable\" id=\"search-Message-1\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"text\" value=\"\"/><div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"sr-only\">41 rows found</div></td></tr></thead></table></div></div><div class=\"dataTables_scrollBody zDocsScrollBodyDiv\" style=\"position: relative; overflow: auto; width: 100%;\"><table class=\"table dataTable no-footer\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1\"><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"height: 0px;\"><th aria-controls=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1\" aria-label=\"\n $dberror value\n : activate to sort column ascending\" class=\"entry sorting\" colspan=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; height: 0px; width: 168.766px;\"><div class=\"dataTables_sizing\" style=\"height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\">\n $dberror value\n </div></th><th aria-controls=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1\" aria-label=\"\n Message\n : activate to sort column ascending\" class=\"entry sorting\" colspan=\"1\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; height: 0px; width: 739.234px;\"><div class=\"dataTables_sizing\" style=\"height: 0px; overflow: hidden;\">\n Message\n </div></th></tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n Success, no error.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n &lt;0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n Error detected by Informix.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 20\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n The requested function/mode is not supported.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 21\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n The specified database environment name is too long.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 22\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n The connector can fetch by primary key only.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 23\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n No more cursors could be allocated.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 24\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n No more statements could be allocated.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 25\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n Connector deleted/updated more or less than 1 row.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 26\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n The parsed SQL statement was not a select.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 27\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n An illegal request was received by the connector.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 28\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n Already logged on to a database.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 29\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n Unrecognized option for open database.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 30\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n No database environment name was specified.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 31\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n Maximum number of logons exceeded.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 32\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n Bad option found in <p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$INF_PARAMS</code>\n</p>.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 33\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n Bad option value found in <p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$INF_PARAMS</code>\n</p>.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 34\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n Mutual exclusive options found in <p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$INF_PARAMS</code>\n</p>.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 35\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n Can’t execute next step. Cursor has been released.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 36\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n Initialization of segmented field in Uniface Virtual Memory failed.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 37\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n Data row size too large.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 38\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n Selection of BLOBs not supported.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 39\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n Data type of existing field does not match BLOB type.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 40\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n Procedure manager raised a DBMS error.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 41\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n CreateProc: The procedure list is not initialized.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 42\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n AllocProcList: Allocation of the procedure list has failed.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 43\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n SetParamPtrs: The parameter value pointers could not be set.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 44\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n Maximum number of connections per logon exceeded.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 45\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n No database name was specified.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 46\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n The database name specified is too long.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 47\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n The specified server name is too long.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 48\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n The specified user name is too long.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 49\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n The specified password name is too long.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 50\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n Sql command buffer overflow.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 51\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n Selected engine does not match specified engine in <p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$INF_PARAMS</code>\n</p>.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 52\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n Overflow tables cannot be created on the fly.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 53\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n Allocation of memory failed.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 54\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n User-defined packing codes: Binary raw storage format not supported.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 55\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n An unknown transaction protocol was requested.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 56\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n Commit or rollback request received when TM is enabled.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row even\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n 100\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n Record/table does not exist.\n </td>\n</tr><tr class=\"row odd\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__1\">\n else\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hsm1665702941775__table_d4742e1_d4743e1_d4744e1__entry__2\">\n No translation for this error code.\n </td>\n</tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"dataTables_scrollFoot\" style=\"overflow: hidden; border: 0px; width: 100%;\"><div class=\"dataTables_scrollFootInner\"><table class=\"table dataTable no-footer\" count-columns=\"2\" style=\"margin-left: 0px;\"><tfoot></tfoot></table></div></div></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528354\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528354\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Informix Error Messages Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Informix Error Messages Both connector and Informix DBMS error and warning messages can be seen in the message frame. The connector may report more than one error or warning at a time. Connector error and warning messages have the following syntax: Connector { ERROR | WARNING } ( Number ) : Message Informix error and warning messages have the following syntax: Informix { ERROR | WARNING | NO DATA } ( SQLSTATE: sqlstate ): Message SQLCODE sqlcode : Message The last error detected by the connector is available in $dberror . The possible error messages are listed in the table. Search: Column $dberror value Message Filter results... 41 rows found Export to Excel Export to CSV Table 1. Error values returned in $dberror $dberror value Message Filter 41 rows found Filter 41 rows found $dberror value Message 0 Success, no error. <0 Error detected by Informix. 20 The requested function/mode is not supported. 21 The specified database environment name is too long. 22 The connector can fetch by primary key only. 23 No more cursors could be allocated. 24 No more statements could be allocated. 25 Connector deleted/updated more or less than 1 row. 26 The parsed SQL statement was not a select. 27 An illegal request was received by the connector. 28 Already logged on to a database. 29 Unrecognized option for open database. 30 No database environment name was specified. 31 Maximum number of logons exceeded. 32 Bad option found in USYS$INF_PARAMS . 33 Bad option value found in USYS$INF_PARAMS . 34 Mutual exclusive options found in USYS$INF_PARAMS . 35 Can’t execute next step. Cursor has been released. 36 Initialization of segmented field in Uniface Virtual Memory failed. 37 Data row size too large. 38 Selection of BLOBs not supported. 39 Data type of existing field does not match BLOB type. 40 Procedure manager raised a DBMS error. 41 CreateProc: The procedure list is not initialized. 42 AllocProcList: Allocation of the procedure list has failed. 43 SetParamPtrs: The parameter value pointers could not be set. 44 Maximum number of connections per logon exceeded. 45 No database name was specified. 46 The database name specified is too long. 47 The specified server name is too long. 48 The specified user name is too long. 49 The specified password name is too long. 50 Sql command buffer overflow. 51 Selected engine does not match specified engine in USYS$INF_PARAMS . 52 Overflow tables cannot be created on the fly. 53 Allocation of memory failed. 54 User-defined packing codes: Binary raw storage format not supported. 55 An unknown transaction protocol was requested. 56 Commit or rollback request received when TM is enabled. 100 Record/table does not exist. else No translation for this error code. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}